


Theme Toggle:
• Use React state to manage the current theme (dark or light).
• When the toggle is clicked, update the theme by adding or removing a CSS class (for example, toggling a light class on the main container or document



Countdown Timer & Progress Bar:
- Implement a 30-second countdown timer that updates every second.
• Display a progress bar that visually indicates the elapsed time.
When the timer reaches zero, display a "Time's Up!" message and automatically toggle the theme.
• Control Buttons:
• Provide a "Start Timer" button to initiate the countdown.
• Provide a "Reset Timer" button that restores the initial state.
• User Experience:
Ensure smooth transitions and animations (for theme changes, progress bar updates, etc.).
• The UI should be same as provided.